expo.description:
This is a simple mobile project created with React Native and TypeScript with the purpose of studying these technologies.

The project consists of a list of participants of some event.

We can:
- Add a participant;
- Remove a participant;
- Remove all participants;
- Add Event details like name and date and remove these data.

In addition, all this data is persistent with Async-Storage, that is, it is saved locally on your device.

It's a project that was developed in Rocketseat's Ignite - React Native bootcamp.
